🇨🇳 Li Fabin 61kg with a 173kg Clean & Jerk to sweep🥇in all categories and break the World Record in the Snatch & Total.

The speed, power, and technique in his lifts are Elite. And you won’t find a lockout and footwork in the split jerk as technically sound as he does it. Eko from 🇮🇩 indonesia in top shape is probably the closest bet at contending for the Olympic Gold  If #teamchina decides to choose Li for the 4th slot.
